@startuml BoraxTheClean_DevelopmentMachine
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor Developer

rectangle "GitHub Actions" as GH {
  rectangle "aws.yml workflow" as Workflow #lightblue
}

rectangle "AWS" as AWS {
  rectangle "CloudFormation" as CF #palegreen
  rectangle "EC2 Instance" as EC2 #lightyellow
  rectangle "IAM Role" as IAM #mistyrose
  rectangle "CloudWatch Alarm" as CW #aliceblue
  rectangle "Security Group" as SG #peachpuff
}

' ========== Connections ==========
Developer --> Workflow : Triggers workflow\nvia push/PR

Workflow --> CF : Deploy stack\nwith parameters
CF --> IAM : Create role\nwith Admin access
CF --> EC2 : Launch instance\nwith IAM role
CF --> SG : Configure\nsecurity group
CF --> CW : Create inactivity\nalarm

EC2 --> CW : Send metrics\n(CPU utilization)
CW --> EC2 : Stop instance\nafter inactivity

' Security concerns
Developer ..> IAM : ! Security risk:\nAdmin access
Developer ..> SG : ! Security risk:\nOpen SSH access
@enduml